item.title: Unlock the Secrets to Easily Transferring Contacts and Apps from iPhone to iPhone!
item.description: IV. Conclusion Introduction Are you ready to upgrade to a new iPhone? If so, you’ll want to make sure that you transfer your contacts and apps from your old device to your new one. Transferring contacts and apps can seem daunting, but it doesn’t have to be! With the right tools and knowledge, you can easily transfer your contacts and apps from your old iPhone to your new one. Definition of “transferring contacts and apps” Transferring contacts and apps from one iPhone to another involves taking your contacts and apps from your old device and moving them to your new device.
